{"about_the_game":"<strong>Dream Bar Simulator</strong> is a next-gen simulator game where you take on the role of a bar owner in a small town.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/MakeDrinksHeader.png?t=1729280967\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/MakeDrinksGiff.gif?t=1729280967\" /><br>Build your menu from a variety of available recipes or create your own. Make quality drinks to keep the customer happy. High-quality drinks lead to happier customers, bigger tips, and a better reputation for your bar. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/ManageResourcesHeader.png?t=1729280967\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/ManageResourcesGiff.gif?t=1729280967\" /><br>In the world of Dream Bar Simulator, you'll find a huge variety of resources to keep your bar stocked. From different alcohol and consumables to furniture and decorations, order goods online or shop local depending on the situation. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/CustomizeYourBarHeader.png?t=1729280967\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/CustomizeGiff.gif?t=1729280967\" /><br>Make your dream bar a reality! Express your unique vision with powerful customization tools. Craft the perfect ambiance to attract the clientele you desire.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/HireEmployeesHeader.png?t=1729280967\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/HireGiff.gif?t=1729280967\" /><br>Delegate tasks and build your dream team! Hire everything from bartenders and servers to security and cleaning staff.  Choose wisely - each potential employee comes with a unique background, personality, and skillset. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/ExpandHeader.png?t=1729280967\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/ExpandGiff.gif?t=1729280967\" /><br>As your bar thrives, expand your territory! Increase your capacity, rake in more profits, and become the hottest spot in town.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Huge selection of drinks and ingredients<br></li><li>Craft original cocktail recipes<br></li><li>Varying drink complexity levels for an extra challenge<br></li><li>Design a unique menu to reflect your bar's style<br></li><li>Recruit staff with unique characteristics and backstories<br></li><li>Deep bar customization options<br></li><li>Maintain order and cleanliness (or don't!)<br></li><li>Deal with drunk customers and the occasional bar brawl! </li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729280967","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1729280967","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/31689238f3180465b4378517e6c01c4269a850fc/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729280967","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/31689238f3180465b4378517e6c01c4269a850fc/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729280967","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_descript